<a data-tip="p$t$liangbianyao" href="/people/liangbianyao">梁边妖</a>，<strong title="偶尔会发笑。" class="zu-question-my-bio">偶尔会发笑。</strong>

</h3>
<a href="javascript:;" name="collapse" class="collapse meta-item zg-right"><i class="z-icon-fold"></i>收起</a>
</div>
<div class="zm-item-vote-info " data-votecount="17004">

<span class="voters">
<span class="user-block">知乎用户、</span><span class="user-block"><a data-tip="p$t$guo-xu-bin" href="http://www.zhihu.com/people/guo-xu-bin" class="zg-link" title="郭旭宾">郭旭宾</a>、</span><span class="user-block"><a data-tip="p$t$ye-ban-li" href="http://www.zhihu.com/people/ye-ban-li" class="zg-link" title="耶板栗">耶板栗</a></span>
</span>


<a href="javascript:;" class="more"> 等人赞同</a>


</div>
