<div class="zm-item-answer-author-info">
<h3 class="zm-item-answer-author-wrap">


<a data-tip="p$t$yunor" href="/people/yunor">yunor</a>，<strong title="神经病" class="zu-question-my-bio">神经病</strong>

</h3>
<a href="javascript:;" name="collapse" class="collapse meta-item zg-right"><i class="z-icon-fold"></i>收起</a>
</div>
<div class="zm-item-vote-info " data-votecount="216">

<span class="voters">
<span class="user-block"><a data-tip="p$t$lu-shu-greene" href="http://www.zhihu.com/people/lu-shu-greene" class="zg-link" title="绿树GREENe">绿树GREENe</a>、</span><span class="user-block"><a data-tip="p$t$qiu-jun-jie-39" href="http://www.zhihu.com/people/qiu-jun-jie-39" class="zg-link" title="裘骏捷">裘骏捷</a>、</span><span class="user-block"><a data-tip="p$t$ieekkza" href="http://www.zhihu.com/people/ieekkza" class="zg-link" title="ieekkza">ieekkza</a></span>
</span>


<a href="javascript:;" class="more"> 等人赞同</a>


